{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840442736,"sessionID":"ses_287a9a86fffe04a1JhL01vrlEY","part":{"id":"prt_d7856a623001y6pJeC6mxJ2IgF","messageID":"msg_d785693f5001uDtPyGlUVsszyg","sessionID":"ses_287a9a86fffe04a1JhL01vrlEY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **AR ID:** AR-001  \n6: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n7: **Language:** Go  \n8: **Size:** S  \n9: \n10: Define the Go type definitions for the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD) under the API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`.\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Requirements\n15: \n16: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD Type Package Structure\n17: \n18: The system SHALL define the AgentRuntime CRD Go types in the package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` following Kubernetes CRD conventions.\n19: \n20: #### Scenario: Package compiles successfully\n21: - **GIVEN** a clean Go module at repository root\n22: - **WHEN** the operator runs `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n23: - **THEN** the package SHALL compile without errors\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Package follows project conventions\n26: - **GIVEN** the package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n27: - **WHEN** inspecting package files\n28: - **THEN** all files SHALL have consistent package naming, proper doc.go documentation, and follow project conventions\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime Root Type Definition\n33: \n34: The system SHALL define an `AgentRuntime` struct that implements the `runtime.Object` interface and includes standard Kubernetes metadata, spec, and status fields.\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime implements runtime.Object\n37: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` struct defined in `agentruntime_types.go`\n38: - **WHEN** the code is compiled\n39: - **THEN** `AgentRuntime` SHALL implement `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` interface\n40: \n41: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime has correct TypeMeta\n42: - **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntime` instance\n43: - **WHEN** accessing its `TypeMeta` fields\n44: - **THEN** `APIVersion` SHALL default to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` and `Kind` SHALL be `AgentRuntime`\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeSpec Definition\n49: \n50: The system SHALL define an `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with fields for `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, and `targetPort` as required fields.\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: Required fields are present\n53: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct definition\n54: - **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n55: - **THEN** it SHALL contain required fields: `maxSessionDuration` (string), `sessionTimeout` (string), `targetPort` (array), and `podTemplate` (PodTemplateSpec)\n56: \n57: #### Scenario: JSON tags use camelCase\n58: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with field tags\n59: - **WHEN** serializing to JSON\n60: - **THEN** field names SHALL use camelCase (e.g., `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, `podTemplate`)\n61: \n62: #### Scenario: Default values are documented\n63: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with kubebuilder markers\n64: - **WHEN** inspecting the markers\n65: - **THEN** `maxSessionDuration` SHALL have default `8h`, and `sessionTimeout` SHALL have default `15m`\n66: \n67: ---\n68: \n69: ### Requirement: TargetPort Sub-resource Definition\n70: \n71: The system SHALL define a `TargetPort` struct representing port configuration with `port` and `protocol` as required fields, and optional `name` and `pathPrefix` fields.\n72: \n73: #### Scenario: TargetPort has required fields\n74: - **GIVEN** the `TargetPort` struct definition\n75: - **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n76: - **THEN** it SHALL contain required `port` (int) and `protocol` (string) fields with kubebuilder validation\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: TargetPort protocol validation\n79: - **GIVEN** the `TargetPort` struct with kubebuilder markers\n80: - **WHEN** validating with `protocol: HTTPS`\n81: - **THEN** it SHALL pass validation (allowed values: HTTP, HTTPS)\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeStatus Definition\n86: \n87: The system SHALL define an `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct with conditions and observed state fields.\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Status has conditions\n90: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct definition\n91: - **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n92: - **THEN** it SHALL contain a `conditions` field of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n93: \n94: #### Scenario: Status subresource marker\n95: - **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` struct with kubebuilder markers\n96: - **WHEN` inspecting the markers\n97: - **THEN** it SHALL include `// +kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ### Requirement: DeepCopy Methods Generation\n102: \n103: The system SHALL include generated DeepCopy methods for all CRD types to support Kubernetes API machinery.\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: DeepCopy methods exist\n106: - **GIVEN** the generated code from `controller-gen`\n107: - **WHEN** inspecting `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n108: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy`, and `DeepCopyObject` methods for `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and `TargetPort`\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ### Requirement: Scheme Registration\n113: \n114: The system SHALL register AgentRuntime types with the runtime scheme.\n115: \n116: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime in scheme\n117: - **GIVEN** the `register.go` file in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n118: - **WHEN** inspecting the `AddToScheme` function\n119: - **THEN** it SHALL register `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types with the scheme builder\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ### Requirement: Code Generation Integration\n124: \n125: The system SHALL integrate with `controller-gen` for generating DeepCopy methods and CRD manifests.\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Controller-gen generates code\n128: - **GIVEN** the `Makefile` with `gen-crd` and `generate` targets\n129: - **WHEN** the operator runs `make generate`\n130: - **THEN** it SHALL invoke `controller-gen object` to generate DeepCopy methods\n131: \n132: ---\n133: \n134: ## File Index\n135: \n136: | Path | Purpose |\n137: |------|---------|\n138: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go` | AgentRuntime type definitions |\n139: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme registration |\n140: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | Package documentation |\n141: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Generated DeepCopy methods |\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ## Dependencies\n146: \n147: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` - Kubernetes metadata types\n148: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` - Runtime.Object interface\n149: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-tools` (controller-gen) - Code generation\n150: \n151: ---\n152: \n153: ## Notes\n154: \n155: - JSON tags SHALL use camelCase per project conventions\n156: - Go structs SHALL use PascalCase per Go conventions\n157: - Kubebuilder markers SHALL follow standard Kubernetes CRD patterns\n158: - The CRD scope SHALL be `Namespaced` (as per deployment/design.md)\n\n(End of file - total 158 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-001  \n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n\nDefine the Go type definitions for the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD) under the API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`.\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD Type Package Structure\n\nThe system SHALL define the AgentRuntime CRD Go types in the package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` following Kubernetes CRD conventions.\n\n#### Scenario: Package compiles successfully","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775840442714,"end":1775840442735}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840442740,"sessionID":"ses_287a9a86fffe04a1JhL01vrlEY","part":{"id":"prt_d7856ab2c001b7RN3sbJF8mrFQ","messageID":"msg_d785693f5001uDtPyGlUVsszyg","sessionID":"ses_287a9a86fffe04a1JhL01vrlEY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 Design: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: Define the Go types for the CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition (CRD).\n6: \n7: ## API Group\n8: \n9: - Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n10: - Version: `v1alpha1`\n11: - Kind: `CodeInterpreter`\n12: \n13: ## Type Definitions\n14: \n15: ### CodeInterpreter\n16: \n17: Root type representing the CodeInterpreter CRD.\n18: \n19: ### CodeInterpreterSpec\n20: \n21: Specification of the desired state for a CodeInterpreter.\n22: \n23: ### CodeInterpreterStatus\n24: \n25: Current observed state of the CodeInterpreter.\n26: \n27: ## Design Decisions\n28: \n29: > TBD: Document key design decisions here.\n30: \n31: ## References\n32: \n33: - [Kubernetes Custom Resources](https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/)\n34: - [Kubebuilder CRD Markers](https://book.kubebuilder.io/reference/markers/crd.html)\n\n(End of file - total 34 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 Design: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nDefine the Go types for the CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition (CRD).\n\n## API Group\n\n- Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n- Kind: `CodeInterpreter`\n\n## Type Definitions\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\nRoot type representing the CodeInterpreter CRD.\n\n### CodeInterpreterSpec\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","time":{"start":1775840442718,"end":1775840442739}}}}
